  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b88\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd - \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf \u0baa\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ruthless Attack on Vaccination Protesters - Lawyer Saliya Peiris",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "Saying that there has been a ruthless attack on the Kota Ko Gama protestors in Kalimugat, the President of the Sri Lankan Bar Association, lawyer Saliya Peiris, has said that this unnecessary and ruthless attack will not help the country in any way and will not help the country's honor internationally.",
        "Several lawyers have reported that there has been an attack on demonstrators near the Presidential Secretariat.",
        "Although the details are not yet fully available, I have information that many people including Nuwan Bobake have been arrested and many others have been assaulted.",
        "He said that the authorities should ensure the safety of everyone and reveal where everyone is kept."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "Saliya Peiris",
          "label": "PERSON"
        }
      ],
